    "name": "Don't Push Me",
    "steam_appid": 1874420,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874420/extras/1defb52836582a22f8a4178cef36614d.avif?t=1768510997\" width=1016 height=664 /></span><strong><br><br>Square off against your friends in this life-or-death shoving simulator!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 Player Local Competitive 1v1. Best played with gamepads. Otherwise, keyboard can be used, and controls are displayed on screen. Keybindings can be re-bound by using the text files in the installation directory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1 vs 1 </strong>- Local Player vs Player Competitive Play. The best way to play!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1 vs AI</strong> - Local training!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>AI vs AI </strong>- Watch two AI duke it out, for fun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To play <strong>ONLINE</strong>, utilize Steam's &quot;Remote Play Together&quot; function. The <strong>Parsec</strong> application is also recommended.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GOAL</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shove your opponent into the spikes on either side of the arena by <strong>DASHING</strong> into them! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each <strong>MATCH</strong> is a &quot;Best of Five&quot;. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >That is, each player has &quot;3 lives&quot;, and the first person to lose all three lives to the spikes loses the match!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MOVES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>JUMP</strong> and <strong>DASH</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DEFAULT CONTROLS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If no controllers or gamepads are plugged in, the game will default to the following keys. You can rebind the default controls using the KeyboardBindings.txt file in the installation directory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Player 1</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MOVEMENT/DIRECTION - W/A/S/D</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >JUMP - G</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DASH - H</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Player 2</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MOVEMENT/DIRECTION - Arrow Keys</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >JUMP - &quot; (quote)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DASH - ; (semicolon)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game By Jakeypoo, @jmanoclay</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Audio By Ian Smith</h2>",
